{"tid":1274411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「請廣傳」聽日開始請暫時離開社交媒體同新聞","createTime":"2019-07-01T16:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T16:34:08.000Z","uid":233929,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59c2cca990a2d86e825d8170f491d38398e92006","tid":1274411,"uid":233929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"過左今晚，<br />\n聽日會有排山倒海既反對聲音，嘲笑同攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n請你暫時離開一切社交媒體/平台同新聞。<br />\n唔係認輸，唔係投降，而係適當既休息。<br />\n做你鐘意做既事，搵你信任既人傾訴陪伴。<br />\n<br />\n保重，我們一直都在，共勉之。"},{"pid":"38ac18f0306d9825a275b981de21104f6d645b6d","tid":1274411,"uid":31151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"點解要離開唔係去抗衡?"},{"pid":"36210657323840fd97c4c28c96e16c35db1c0bf1","tid":1274411,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"鋼鐵般既意志"},{"pid":"704a94973c4704fed0f6c23cbef3d2ebb6459b01","tid":1274411,"uid":233929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ac18f0306d9825a275b981de21104f6d645b6d","tid":1274411,"uid":31151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"點解要離開唔係去抗衡?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}